com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.list

Class StackArrayList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.list.StackArrayList<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.List<T>

    public class StackArrayList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.List<T>
    This list works like Stack, when you add a element, it will be added in the left-side of list If you remove a element, all elements will be moved to left-side
